      "bullets": [
        "Moonshot’s Kimi K3 and Alibaba’s Qwen series signal rapid progress in Chinese frontier-class LLMs, focusing heavily on advanced reasoning capabilities.",
        "Anthropic faces headwinds amid rumored talent departures, compute allocation strains, and pressure to deliver a definitive Claude 3.5 Opus successor.",
        "The competitive landscape highlights a structural shift from raw pre-training scale to RL-based test-time compute and inference-time scaling search."
      ]
