      "bullets": [
        "Leverage server-side Git post-receive hooks in bare repositories to trigger automated builds and deployments without external CI/CD servers.",
        "Execute isolated test suites and linters via shell scripts, utilizing custom environment variables and SSH keys for secure production deployments.",
        "Ideal for solo developers or micro-projects seeking zero-dependency, ultra-fast pipelines, bypassing resource-heavy platforms like GitHub Actions or GitLab CI."
